reviews_data.review_text:
I'm always in search of a good milk tea and this place was...alright. Me and my husband both got oolong milk teas, no customization, no boba. The tea flavor overall was a little bit weak, very dairy forward. But it was smooth and there was plenty of ice. A good pick me up after a long day.

Menu was well-rounded, with options for coffee and fruit-based drinks. I wish there were options for alternative milks like oat or almond, though.

It felt a little like the woman working that day seemed a little lost on the menu. I had to repeat my order twice before she understood me. She also seemed confused about the cinnamon muffin my husband ordered, asking her coworker several times if they even had those in the pastry case.

This is the absolute worst excuse for a coffee shop!! I waited 30+ mins for a drink that I never even received. Since it is a family business they have untrained minor children (presumably the owners kids) in there working as baristas. They are terrible. Every single transaction was done incorrectly. Another customer with a terrible experience like mine, requested a refund. They refunded a her drink to a different customers card. It’s so awful. I will not be returning and will be sure to spread the word amongst my coffee loving friends that this is a terrible TERRIBLE place to go for coffee.
I got the Brown Sugar Coffee Latte and it was delicious. I would recommend this spot to anyone.

I got a Vietnamese coffee with cream and it was SOOO good. I live near Matthews and I am craving another one so I am going again tomorrow. (They aren't open on Mondays 😞)
My daughter got a Boba tea and her only regret was that she should jave bought the larger size  She loved it!
Amazing boba drinks. I especially love the brown sugar milk tea!
Great place! Good Vietnamese sandwiches, coffee, and specialty drinks.
My drink was sweeter than expected, yet very flavorful. I’ll be back to try new flavors.
I get the ube latte every time I come here. It's the best ube latte I've ever had. They make it with Vietnamese coffee and I tend to like a stronger coffee flavor so it's perfect for me!
Delicious boba and tea!!
We have tasted boba tea across the country and this is one of best! Definitely coming back! The mango is amazing!

Tried one of their boba tea for first time though door dash. The drink was ok. There was to much ice,the matcha flavor was not strong and the boba was nice and chewy but had no flavor. So might not get milk tea from there again but may try something else.
Delicious!!!
A cozy little shop with the most perfect Thai milk tea! Definitely a good spot to stop with friends!
My God I love the coffee here. Starbucks is in danger right now of me switching. It was so good I had to go back 30 minutes later. ❤️❤️❤️❤️

Beautiful setting, many options to choose from.

Love how small and simple Cafe giving a calm and relaxed vibe. Importantly, the place is clean, fast, and friendly staff. I ordered a large ice black coffee, and it is naturally sweet tasting overall.
Drinks is a 10 out of 10

Taste as good as it looks
